PhQ::Internal::Conversion< Unit, UnitValue > Class Template Reference

Abstract class for converting a value expressed in a unit of measure to or from the standard unit of measure of that type. Internal implementation detail not intended to be used outside of the PhQ::Convert, PhQ::ConvertCopy, and PhQ::StaticConvertCopy functions. More...

Detailed Description

template<typename Unit, Unit UnitValue>
class PhQ::Internal::Conversion< Unit, UnitValue >

Abstract class for converting a value expressed in a unit of measure to or from the standard unit of measure of that type. Internal implementation detail not intended to be used outside of the PhQ::Convert, PhQ::ConvertCopy, and PhQ::StaticConvertCopy functions.
